Analyte(s): Thyroid stimulating autoantibodies to TSH receptors
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Thyretain TM TSI Reporter BioAssay for qualitative detection of thyroid stimulating autoantibodies in serum as an aid in the differential diagnosis of Graves' disease.
Indications for Use Summary: Qualitative detection in serum of thyroid stimulating autoantibodies to TSH receptors as an aid in the differential diagnosis of patients with Graves' disease.
